| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-2624 — Mass File Rename (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 240b01a3-9d00-57e1-96dd-fdfb382507eb"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
